not been trained on by\nperforming a transferability analysis. Our model allows optimal selection of\n2D-substrate pairings to maximize heat transfer and will improve thermal\nmanagement in future 2D nanoelectronics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Jan 2023 03:46:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-22"}
