ng its spin-momentum locking property. This\nlab-based LMS-ARPES will be a powerful research tool for studying the local\nfine electronic structures of different condensed matter systems, including\ntopological quantum materials, mesoscopic materials and structures, and\nphase-separated materials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Jan 2023 12:40:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-22"}
